# Blackjack Game (C++ Terminal Version)

## 🃏 About the Game
This is a simple Blackjack game implemented in C++ that runs in the terminal. The game follows standard Blackjack rules, where the goal is to get a hand value as close to 21 as possible without exceeding it.

## 🎮 Features
- Single-player mode against the dealer
- Standard Blackjack rules
- Hit, Stand, and Bust mechanics
- Random card generation
- User-friendly terminal interface
